Package com.ab.utilities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataProviderUtil
    The DataProviderUtil class is a utility class that provides test data for TestNG tests using the @DataProvider annotation.
    DateUtil
    The DateUtil class provides methods to manipulate dates and times.
    DynamicXpathUtil
    The DynamicXpathUtil class provides a method to build dynamic XPath expressions.
    ExcelUtil
    The ExcelUtil class provides methods to read data from an Excel file.
    PropertiesUtil
    The PropertiesUtil class contains utility methods for working with properties files.
    ScreenShotsUtil
    The ScreenShotsUtil class contains a utility method for capturing screenshots in Base64 format.
    StringsUtil
    The StringsUtil class contains utility methods for working with strings.
